Key Match Events: Albert Gronbaek scored the first goal for Denmark after a one-two exchange with Yussuf Poulsen
Yussuf Poulsen scored a bicycle kick for the second goal for Denmark
Post-Match Reflections: Lars Knudsen, Denmark's caretaker coach, praised his team's performance
Miscellaneous Highlights: Denmark has 13 straight undefeated games on home soil in the UEFA Nations League
Others: Serbia has a significant task ahead of them after holding reigning champions Spain to a goalless draw on UNL matchday one
